title: Single family home in desirable Cuesta Park area of Mountain V
posting_body: ['Four bedrooms, two baths single family home located in desirable Cuesta Park area of Mountain View.', 'Large Living/dining room with fireplace and sliding doors facing the backyard.', 'Gourmet Granite kitchen includes refrigerator, dishwasher, new GE gas burner cooktop and hood, oven, microwave and a large breakfast nook area with bay window facing the backyard.', 'Master Bedroom with separate shower stall, new vanity, flooring, medicine cabinet and toilet.', 'New vanity, Toilet and flooring in bathroom #2.', 'All rooms are large and bright.', 'Extra large fourth bedroom can be used as family/entertainment room.', 'Pantry & Laundry room equipped with new GE Washer and Dryer.', 'New flooring in the Laundry room.', 'DSL and cable/satellite TV available.', 'A separate large storage room located in the beautifully landscaped backyard with fruit trees.', 'Fenced back yard.', 'New Roof, gutter and down Spots.', 'Central Heating.', 'Weekly gardening fee included in rent.', 'Excellent neighborhood with award winning schools (Bubb, Graham and Mountain View High).', 'Walking distance to Cuesta Park and several shopping centers.', 'Close to El Camino Hospital and YMCA (has Child Care center).', 'Quite neighborhood with short access to major highways (85, 280, 237, and 101)', 'Rent is $5800 per month.', 'Available August 6th.']
